These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
2 different games are played: billiard, domino
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the person playing domino##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | domino   | billiard  |
| Sport   | soccer | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: american, italian
2 different pets are kept: goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the goat is not the italian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | american | italian      |
| Pet    | goat  | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, pumpkin
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, snowmobile
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating plum##1
2. the person driving the van is not the person eating plum##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | pumpkin  | plum    |
| Sport   | van | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, grapefruit
City: hannover, miami
1. the person eating grapefruit is not the person traveling to hannover##6
2. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person eating apricot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | apricot  | grapefruit |
| Pet    | hannover | miami    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
