.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, social-worker
2 different games are played: chess, go
1. the accountant is in an odd position##4
2. the accountant is not the person playing go##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | accountant | social-worker |
| Pet   | chess       | go       |

